NK037(ji)004:0: de nas drag po'i rjes gnang ni /
NK037(ji)004:1: lcags khang dmigs rten byas pa'i mthar //
NK037(ji)004:2: drag po'i rdzas rnams bkram par bya //
NK037(ji)004:3: mgon po 'khor bcas bskyed bstim bskul //
NK037(ji)004:4: yon tan brjod la sbyin par bya //
NK037(ji)004:5: bsnyen sgrub rim pa'i sngags brjod cing //
NK037(ji)004:6: man ngag thams cad rdzogs par sbyin //
NK037(ji)004:7: sangs rgyas kun gyi ral gri che //
NK037(ji)004:9: dgra bgegs gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:10: de ring bu yis blang bar bya //
NK037(ji)004:11: badz+ra kham a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:12: ti ra beng chen gsal shing 'di //
NK037(ji)004:13: srid gsum dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK037(ji)004:14: gdug pa rdul du brlag bya'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:15: de ring bu yis blang bar bya //
NK037(ji)004:16: ti ra rat+na d+h+aa ka dz+wa la a bi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:18: dug lnga dbyings su bsgral ba dang //
NK037(ji)004:19: sdig can lnga phung bshig pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:20: de ring bu yis blang bar bya //
NK037(ji)004:21: badz+ra a ba d+ha ab+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:22: drag po gnam lcags phur bu 'di //
NK037(ji)004:23: dbyings nas ye shes shar ba dang //
NK037(ji)004:24: zhing bcu gnas su bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK037(ji)004:25: de ring bu yis badz+ra k+ai la ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:26: thod rlon gdug pa'i khrag gis bkang //
NK037(ji)004:27: 'khor ba dong nas sprugs pa dang //
NK037(ji)004:28: dam nyams snying khrag 'thung ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:29: de ring bu yis ka p+aa la rak+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:30: mdung rnon g.yang gzhi ru mtshon 'di //
NK037(ji)004:31: bdud kyi g.yul las rgyal ba dang //
NK037(ji)004:32: ban dgra'i snying gzer gdab pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:33: de ring bu yis badz+ra sh+au la a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:35: 'khor bcas gnas nas drangs pa dang //
NK037(ji)004:36: dgra srog yan lag bsdom pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:37: de ring bu yis n+aa ga p+aa sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:38: chos sku yon tan mchog mnga' ba'i //
NK037(ji)004:39: phyag mtshan drag po tsa ma ra //
NK037(ji)004:40: dam can gnas nas 'go ba'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:41: de ring bu yis badz+ra tsa ma ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:42: legs ldan khro rgyal thugs ka nas //
NK037(ji)004:43: sar sha pa ni mtshon cha mchog /
NK037(ji)004:44: yungs kar rgyal po sha r+ai ram //
NK037(ji)004:45: de ring bu yis badz+ra be t+aa li rak+sha yak+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:46: gu gul sbyar ba'i rdzas mchog 'di //
NK037(ji)004:47: dgra bo lha dang dbye ba dang //
NK037(ji)004:48: bgegs rnams myos nas bskrad pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:49: de ring bu yis ma gu ta la pra ta la a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:50: ri rab gling bzhi rgya gram 'di //
NK037(ji)004:51: rtog pa'i zug rngu gzhil ba dang //
NK037(ji)004:52: gdug pa can rnams mnan pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:53: de ring bu yis b+hi shwa badz+ra sum e bam m+aa y+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:55: nyon mongs 'khor ba bag chags dang //
NK037(ji)004:56: dgra bgegs thams cad bsreg pa'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:57: de ring bu yis badz+ra dz+wa la ram a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK037(ji)004:58: thabs shes chags sdang mda' gzhu dang //
NK037(ji)004:59: drag po'i thun zor dam rdzas 'di //
NK037(ji)004:60: dgra bgegs rdul du brlag bya'i phyir //
NK037(ji)004:61: de ring bu yis blang bar bya //
